videos.description: Brandon Ingram drives between defenders and drops in a floater while drawing contact.

videos.headline: Ingram splits defenders for the and-1

videos.description: Lonzo Ball lobs the ball from near half court to Zion Williamson for a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lonzo's long lob finds Zion for the jam) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lonzo's long lob finds Zion for the jam

videos.description: Julius Randle pulls up from mid-range and knocks down the jumper while being fouled.
videos.headline: Randle smoothly sinks and-1

videos.description: Zion Williamson splits between two defenders and then throws down a thunderous one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion emphatically drops the hammer) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion emphatically drops the hammer

videos.description: Zion Williamson flies to the bucket and Eurosteps his way for an and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion roars after Eurostep and-1) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion roars after Eurostep and-1

videos.description: Eric Bledose lobs it up in transition to Zion Williamson, who throws down a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bledsoe and Zion connect for alley-oop in transition) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bledsoe and Zion connect for alley-oop in transition

videos.description: Julius Randle drops in a nice step-back jumper over Zion Williamson.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Randle cooks up step-back over Zion) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randle cooks up step-back over Zion

videos.description: Reggie Bullock ties the game late with a 3-pointer and then Eric Bledsoe misses a game-winner as time expires to send the game to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bullock's 3-pointer helps send game to OT) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bullock's 3-pointer helps send game to OT

videos.description: Julius Randle makes his way to the bucket and then lobs it up to Nerlens Noel for a two-handed dunk.

videos.headline: Randle dishes to Noel for alley-oop

videos.description: Brandon Ingram tries to throw down a two-handed dunk, but Nerlens Noel jumps high to deny the attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Noel rises up to deny Ingram's dunk attempt) 2021/04/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Noel rises up to deny Ingram's dunk attempt

videos.description: Stan Van Gundy is adamant that the Pelicans had no business losing the way they did against the Knicks.
